# Questions

There are 5 types of question indicated by the <code>question-type</code> attribute.

* __Boolean__ - true or false

* __Choice__ - array of alternatives. If <code>multiple</code> is true multiple answers are allowed. Otherwise only one.

* __Text__ - free text answers

* __Range__ - answer could be a number within the range defined by <code>start-with</code> and <code>end-with</code>. The unit contains the range unit (i.e year or pieces).

* __Video__ - answer with a video

## Question Object

```json
{
  "id": "1337",
  "type": "questions",
  "links": {
    "self": "http://api.teamtailor.dev/v1/questions/1337"
  },
  "attributes": {
    "alternatives": null,
    "end-with": null,
    "multiple": null,
    "question-type": "Text",
    "start-with": null,
    "title": "Can you describe your ideal work environment?",
    "unit": null
  }
}
```

### Attributes

Attribute     | Type    | Description
--------------|---------|------------
alternatives  | array   |
